      "content": "i don't even want \"different care.\" i just want it to stop. i'm tired of being a burden on everyone, even the nurses, and i'm tired of my body failing me every single day. it feels like there's no dignity left in just sitting here, waiting for some natural end that might take years of suffering to finally arrive. it feels like i've lost all control over my own life.",
